          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-copy-1639394705293-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the rice is cooking, cut your <strong>Tenderstem broccoli </strong>in half</p><p>Cut a piece<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>of <strong>tin foil</strong> approx. the size of A3 paper (or two!)</p><p>Lay the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>Tenderstem</strong> in the middle with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and add to a baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Scrunch the edges of the foil around the Tenderstem to form a sealed parcel[s] and put the tray[s] in the oven for 15 min or until tender</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1639394708650-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1639394708650-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-1639394708650-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
