            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> lengthways into 2 strips per person, then cut each strip in half</p><p>Add the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>cornflour</strong> to a bowl along with 1 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong>, your <strong>five-spice mix </strong>and a generous grind of<strong> black pepper </strong>and mix it all together</p><p>Add the <strong>basa strips</strong> to the bowl and give everything a good mix up until all the basa is coated</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-1639394722656-x200.jpg",
