            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once the pan is very hot, add the <strong>coated basa strips</strong> along with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>soy sauce</strong> and cook for 5-6 min on each side until golden and crispy and the basa is cooked through – this is your <strong>crispy basa</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p><p>Once crispy, transfer to a plate and set aside (save the pan for later!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-1639394725121-x200.jpg",
